{"tid":579122,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［召喚連登醫生］向左轉會眩暈","createTime":"2018-03-03T10:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T10:12:38.000Z","uid":31002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcd0738f71fe7c6c562d020d4dc9e93772378fe","tid":579122,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"星期一係電腦凳轉左陣<br />\n之後就有少少暈，去到星期四起身覺得天旋地轉<br />\n暈到想嘔，行唔到直線咁<br />\n食左止暈藥好少少，都仲係覺得啲野順時針咁轉<br />\n有冇巴打知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26b965b72dbaa077c2579ad3b49f97566471d2e","tid":579122,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"耳石脫落"},{"pid":"7cf208114bedb2ccc1825e0c6f6bbe1538d9f1a5","tid":579122,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"唔轉番右？"},{"pid":"0722ebef21baa114cfb5a684e3398e39c98b4f23","tid":579122,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e26b965b72dbaa077c2579ad3b49f97566471d2e","tid":579122,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"耳石脫落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得似係，但做咗網上啲練習都冇乜用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要趕assignment，集中唔到呀救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a600e8f37b5f54e76ca77a6793ffb2830219e4","tid":579122,"uid":61193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"常見單邊暈既原因有benign paroxysmal positional vertigo, 即係耳石移位<br />\n同埋meniere disease, 即係耳水不平衡<br />\n你去搵個醫生睇，等佢幫你檢查先知係咩事"},{"pid":"4a32809acf848130c7d183bb21657b5b1349b39b","tid":579122,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a600e8f37b5f54e76ca77a6793ffb2830219e4","tid":579122,"uid":61193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:04